<p>
<lb n="1"/>śrīparvata malēśvara dēvaraku 
<lb n="2"/>nijamūlabhṛtulaina vidyādharama 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>hāpātṛla dharmamu I gōpuraṁ śēI 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ṁcina Adhikāri lakuṇadēvu taṁḍri gōvi 
<lb n="5" break="no"/>da dēvu taṁḍri ravidēvu taṁḍri haridēvu <unclear>vī</unclear> 
<lb n="6" break="no"/><unclear>rikigā</unclear> manumaṁḍu dōmāIdēvu śrī 
<lb n="7" break="no"/>śrīdaṇarautu koḍuku kāḷidāsu 
<lb n="8"/>rautu koḍuku śrīpati koḍuku kē 
<lb n="9" break="no"/>śava koḍuku Igōpuraṁ śēśina Āsa 
<lb n="10" break="no"/>ri nāgaramāharaṇa 
</p>

